		{
			dependencies: ["0232486D4EEE2A9A"]
			description: [
				"Cleaning pollution can be tiring and time consuming, so you want to automate the proccess somehow."
				""
				"This is where Filters comes in: they can collect pollution blocks by using respective resources."
				"- For &lcarbon&r you need to put &oleaves&r in the filter."
				"- For &lsulfur&r you need &owool&r blocks."
				""
				"The result of this will be black and yellow dyes and fresh air in your factory!"
