		{
			dependencies: ["7D3FA2BBD1033FE9"]
			description: [
				"Solid boilers will generate steam for your first simple machinery."
				""
				"They need constant inflow of water to not explode. If you still choose to filling it manually then be careful: &oif boiler will heat up to maximum adding water is strictly &lprohibited!&r You need wait for it to cool down.  "
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
