		{
			dependencies: ["4EC3B664D62760BE"]
			description: [
				"This type of boilers have different variations depending on its size. Maximum amount fireboxes are 3x3. With each size level amount of minimum boilers grows. You can start with 1 firebox and boiler."
				""
				"They much more efficent than bronze and high pressure ones, but need fuel and &lconstant supply of WATER.&r If you will not provide it and boiler get too heated, trying adding more will make it EXPLODE. "
			]
