			dependencies: ["4EBBAB4B8A99D4A7"]
			description: [
				"Spice of Life: Apple Pie Edition adds ability to gain benefits for eating large and tasty meals. &l&oIt will not punish you for eating the same food normaly.&r That way you will not suffer in early stages when there not much too eat, but if you want some useful buffs later you can try to make meals from &oPam's Harvestcraft&r."
				""
				"Instead of normal grass, Pam's Harvestcraft crops drop from special biome related gardens. When you break them you will get various seeds and vegetables. "
