		{
			dependencies: ["3129F95624CBEDD4"]
			description: [
				"Crafting Blueprint is a block much like a painting that can be used to save crafting recipes and auto craft them easily. It can cover up to a 3x3 wall area."
				""
				"Right click a slot to open the interface and use items to save a crafting recipe. Filters can also be used to apply multiple potential crafting recipes."
				""
				"Outside the interface, right click the saved recipe to use available materials to craft the item. Shift right click to craft up to a stack of the item. Left click to delete a crafting recipe. A secondary display slot is available for each slot."
				""
				"&oThis can be very useful in crafting of many Gregtech components.&r"
			]
			id: "191FA67C7B17BB2F"
